{"tid":1396676,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特許金融分析師(CFA)要求香港特區政府回應民間五大訴求","createTime":"2019-08-02T07:30:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T03:20:12.000Z","uid":212453,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4f81f34f87f583280a912f4e7573edef718a2fd8","tid":1396676,"uid":212453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:30:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QbKDOLX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQbKDOLX.png&h=0a3cc4e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[代金融𨶙post]<br />\n<br />\n[For immediate release together with CFA Charterholders&rsquo; endorsement]<br />\n<br />\n2 August 2019<br />\n<br />\n各位香港市民：<br />\n<br />\n我們是一班持有特許金融分析師(CFA)資格認證，並任職於各大銀行、資產管理、投資公司等金融機構的業界從業員。<br />\n<br />\n作為特許金融分析師協會 (CFA Institute)的一份子，我等致力維護誠信和道德標準。我們深信這套專業操守與日常生活上每一個環節密不可分。<br />\n<br />\n過去兩個月來，香港警方於多宗反對《逃犯條例》修訂事件中對示威者使用過分武力。相反，對於721元朗暴徒襲擊事件卻袖手旁觀。這套雙重標準實有違專業道德，對社會的破壞遠比逃犯條例對香港的影響深遠。<br />\n<br />\n我們在此強烈要求香港特區政府回應民間五大訴求，包括：<br />\n<br />\n1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 全面撤回逃犯條例修訂<br />\n2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 撤回「暴動」定性<br />\n3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 馬上停止對反送中抗爭者的政治檢控<br />\n4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 成立由資深法官領導的獨立調查委員會，追究濫用武力及違規的警務人員<br />\n5.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 落實真普選<br />\n<br />\n投資策略在於權衡交易風險及回報的時機。我們相信現在就是最好的時機與香港人同行，建設更美好的香港。我們促請香港以至全球各地擁有特許金融分析師(CFA)資格認證的人士向各界表達香港人對公義的追求。<br />\n<br />\n只要各界攜手合作，我們不僅可以為香港帶來更好的經濟環境，更可鞏固香港自由及法治的基石，讓香港的繁榮延續下去。<br />\n<br />\n一群熱愛香港並持有特許金融分析師(CFA)資格認證的市民敬上"},{"pid":"69845aba920724fb69cae54f74538cbbc6f98e33","tid":1396676,"uid":259842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:31:53.000Z","msg":"ho ball"},{"pid":"a0c15eb06f2a128182db2632cb922520d4389389","tid":1396676,"uid":259842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:32:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"231447d1077d4d5be8a408f6caab1789082f83b0","tid":1396676,"uid":48667,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:32:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3da5ef3217d89f32442f5965909bcac1c0a6abda","tid":1396676,"uid":235278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:34:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbb2b45641e48938006cdae87c13e4e64ca0cb6b","tid":1396676,"uid":17154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:34:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7ee1dd6ead52fe82fc583973bb38dae101be099","tid":1396676,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:36:27.000Z","msg":"多謝!"},{"pid":"c31cc5ee1378fc8e3594e9a2d6b012f026faaa9d","tid":1396676,"uid":113024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:45:26.000Z","msg":"I want to show my support and send my cert...where is the link/contact etc?<br />\n<br />\np.s. CFA since 2010"},{"pid":"ebd09ca0e22f86941cf87267edd6e1a8812bd131","tid":1396676,"uid":212453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c31cc5ee1378fc8e3594e9a2d6b012f026faaa9d","tid":1396676,"uid":113024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:45:26.000Z","msg":"I want to show my support and send my cert...where is the link/contact etc?<br />\n<br />\np.s. CFA since 2010"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:20:12.000Z","msg":"Hey mate , tg is the safest way to communicate . Could you download one ?"}]}